---
import "../styles/style.css";
---

<section id="quiz_game">
  <article>
    <h1>Escape from reality and step into the</h1>
    <div class="animation">
      <lottie-player id="playroom" src="playroom.json" background="transparent" speed="1" style="width: 300px; height: 300px;"></lottie-player>

      <script>
        LottieInteractivity.create({
          player: "#playroom",
          mode: "scroll",
          container: "#MyContainer",
          actions: [
            {
              visibility: [0, 1.0],
              type: "seek",
              frames: [0, 178],
            },
          ],
        });
      </script>
    </div>
    <div class="text">
      <p>
        Step into the <span>p</span>layroom, where even though former kings <span>a</span>nd queens used to pla<span>y</span> here, it is not all fun and games. <span>C</span>an you solve the puzzles and figure out what wrongs have been committed and
        who till this day still haunts th<span>e</span> queen. Wil<span>l</span> you escape , or will you become part of the royal doll collection. D<span>o</span> you have the courage and i<span>m</span>agination it takes to figure out what secrets
        the playroom is hiding.
      </p>
      <div class="code">
        <button id="Mycontainer">Kampaign code</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
<style>
  h1 {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;

    margin-top: 50px;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 150px;
  }
  span {
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  section {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--three);

    margin-top: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 200px;
  }
  article {
    background-color: var(--one);
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  lottie-player {
    margin-top: -15%;
    margin-bottom: -5%;
  }

  .text {
    margin-inline: 10%;
  }

  .animation {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  lottie-player {
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
  }

  .code {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  button {
    font-family: "open-sans", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--one);
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    cursor: pointer;

    border: none;
    background: var(--six);
    height: 60px;
    width: 215px;
    border-radius: 10px;

    margin-bottom: 100px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    section {
      margin-inline: 10%;

      margin-bottom: 150px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 30%;
      margin-top: 10%;
    }

    lottie-player {
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;

      margin-top: -15%;
      margin-bottom: -10%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    section {
      margin-inline: 5%;
    }

    article {
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-inline: -10%;
    }
    lottie-player {
      margin-top: -20%;
      margin-bottom: -15%;

      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>
